---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Revenue Recovery + Growth for Trades Businesses — $2,500/mo | BrandsBuilders',
  description: 'In your missed calls and old customer list there\'s $15–30k/year sitting on the floor. We recover it in the first 2 weeks — and that pays for the system that brings new clients. $2,500/mo. No setup fee. No contract.',
  canonical: 'https://brandsbuilders.ca',
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-14 pb-16 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">

      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 text-sm font-semibold mb-8">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0 animate-pulse"></span>
        1 spot available this week
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-[1.08] tracking-tight">
        Your missed calls and old customer list are hiding
        <span class="text-orange-600"> $15–30k a year on the floor.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-7 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We recover it in the first 2 weeks — without spending on ads. That pays for the system that brings new clients every month.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/apply"
          class="inline-flex px-9 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 transition text-lg shadow-sm">
          See if I qualify →
        </a>
        <a href="https://cal.com/brandsbuilders/30-min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex px-9 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 border border-gray-300 hover:border-gray-400 transition text-lg">
          Talk first
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-gray-400">
        $2,500/mo · No setup fee · No long-term contract
      </p>

      <!-- stat row -->
      <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-6 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">$15–30k</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">lost per year to missed calls and inactive customers</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-6 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-600">2 weeks</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">to see the first recovered jobs booked</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-6 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">30 days</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">or we work free until the guarantee is met</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ GUARANTEE ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">The Guarantee</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        If we don't generate more in booked jobs than you paid us in 30 days — we work free until we do.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        How it's measured (no arguments): booked jobs attributed to the system — calls and texts through the tracked number + reactivation campaign replies — with estimated value over $2,500 in the month. All visible in your dashboard, not in anyone's memory.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-left max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-3">Your only part of the deal:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300 text-sm">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            You answer or return leads within 24 hours
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300 text-sm">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            You give us access in week 1
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4">We can't recover calls nobody returns. The risk is on us — not you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ HOW IT WORKS ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">How the system works</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-gray-600">Two phases. First we recover what's already yours. Then we grow.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 border border-orange-200 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 1 — Weeks 1 & 2</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Recovery · No ad spend</span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Week 1</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">You'll know exactly how much money is leaking</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Full funnel audit + tracked number setup + dashboard. Missed-Call Recovery live in 48 hours: every missed call gets an automatic text back within seconds.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Week 2</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">First recovered jobs booked — without ads</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Reactivation campaign to your existing base: unclosed estimates, customers from 1–2 years ago. Automated follow-up on new incoming leads.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-gray-900 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 2 — Week 3 onwards</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Growth · New clients</span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {[
            { week: 'Week 3', title: 'Your site converts', desc: 'Landing page optimization + end-to-end tracking. Every sale attributed to its real source.' },
            { week: 'Week 4', title: 'Campaign live', desc: 'Full ad setup + creatives + launch. First qualified leads coming in.' },
            { week: 'Month 2', title: 'Real ROI — not guesses', desc: '6+ weeks of data vs. your week-1 baseline. Creatives and landing improving continuously.' },
            { week: 'Month 3+', title: 'We scale what works', desc: 'Budget scaling based on your unit economics — not gut feelings.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">{item.week}</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHAT'S INCLUDED ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-y border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">$2,500/mo covers all our work</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-lg">Ad spend goes separately — straight from your card to Google/Meta, in accounts you own.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        {[
          { icon: 'M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z', label: 'Missed-call recovery system', desc: 'Tracked number + auto-SMS within seconds, 24/7' },
          { icon: 'M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15', label: 'Reactivation campaigns', desc: 'SMS + email to your inactive customer list' },
          { icon: 'M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z', label: 'Full ads management', desc: 'Google or Meta — setup, creatives, ongoing optimization' },
          { icon: 'M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z', label: 'Tracking + real reporting', desc: 'Dashboard with every lead, its source, and estimated value' },
          { icon: 'M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z', label: 'Website / landing optimization', desc: 'Continuous CRO — your landing page improves every week' },
          { icon: 'M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z', label: 'Direct access — no tickets', desc: 'My personal number, response under 24h, Monday to Monday' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={item.icon}/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">{item.label}</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5 leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-xl p-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-sm text-orange-900 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>About ad spend:</strong> The first 2–4 weeks you spend nothing on ads. The recovery phase works on what you already have. Ads turn on in phase 2 — ideally paid for by what phase 1 already generated. Recommended budget when we get there: <strong>$1,500–2,500/mo</strong>.
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHO THIS IS FOR ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Who this is for</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">You're a fit if...</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Your business does $1M–$3M in annual revenue',
              'You\'re in trades: plumbing, HVAC, roofing, electrical, landscaping, cleaning, or similar',
              'You have an existing customer base — even 50–200 people',
              'You can return leads within 24 hours',
              'You want predictable growth — not just putting out fires',
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-red-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Not for you if...</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'You just started and have no past customers',
              'You don\'t have time or willingness to return calls',
              'You want results without giving access or context',
              'Your average job value is under $500',
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ SOCIAL PROOF ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 border-y border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-8">
        {[
          { text: 'He actually listens, understands the day-to-day challenges we face, and delivers solutions that are practical, efficient, and tailored — not generic. He doesn\'t just talk strategy, he executes.', name: 'Heaven Artisan GF' },
          { text: 'Clean layout and helped increase revenue for my business.', name: 'Abdul B.' },
          { text: 'Local, friendly, and brings results over the expectation. Highly recommended.', name: 'Justice Rayy' },
        ].map(r => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-yellow-400 mb-3">
              {Array.from({length: 5}).map(() => (
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.802 2.035a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.802-2.035a1 1 0 00-1.175 0L6.62 16.282c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.984 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">"{r.text}"</p>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-gray-200 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900">{r.name} <span class="text-gray-400 font-normal">· Google Review</span></div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/proof" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 font-medium transition">See all projects and reviews →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FAQ ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-10">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        {[
          { q: 'Why $2,500/mo if ad spend isn\'t included?', a: 'The $2,500 covers all our work: system installation, full management, creatives, continuous optimization, reporting, and direct access to me. Ad spend goes straight to Google or Meta — in accounts you own. We don\'t touch that money or mark it up. If you ever leave, everything stays with you.' },
          { q: 'What happens if I don\'t see results in 30 days?', a: 'We work the next month free until the guarantee is met. The measurement is clear: booked jobs through the tracked number and reactivation replies with value over $2,500. Everything in your dashboard — no disputes.' },
          { q: 'How much time do I have to put in?', a: 'About 3 hours during initial setup for access and feedback. After that, you return leads within 24 hours and spend 1 hour a month reviewing reporting. The point of the system is that it works without you on top of it.' },
          { q: 'Is there a long-term contract?', a: 'No. No setup fee. No cancellation penalty. If at any point the system doesn\'t make sense for your business, let us know and it\'s closed. No fees, no paperwork.' },
          { q: 'When do I start spending on ads?', a: 'Week 3 or 4 — once your landing is ready and tracking is confirmed working. The first 2 weeks the recovery phase works without spending on ads.' },
          { q: 'Why only 1 client per week?', a: 'The system gets installed properly or it doesn\'t. I take time to understand your business, your numbers, and your market — that can\'t be done in series. If this week\'s spot is taken, the next start is next week.' },
        ].map(f => (
          <details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center gap-4 text-sm">
              {f.q}
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{f.a}</p>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FINAL CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-orange-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">The 30-second pitch</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        Every call your business misses is a $5–30k job going to your competitor.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We install a system that recovers those calls and reactivates your old customers — in 2 weeks, without spending on ads. And if in any month we don't generate more than you pay us, the next month is on us until we do. You can't lose — either the system pays for itself, or we work free.
      </p>
      <a href="/apply"
        class="inline-flex px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-lg">
        See if I qualify →
      </a>
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-gray-500">
        Only 1 spot available this week
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</LandingLayout>
